stories.text:
Hello everybody,

Out of fun, I made a job board, https://www.pacificdevs.com, dedicated to the IT sector in AUS/NZ. Primarily I did this project to improve my skills and I was wondering if there is something I could improve. So far it features:

- Filters to search by tags, location, visa sponsorship, remote, etc. - Companies can post job offers with a description, tech stack as well as benefits (work from home, pet friendly office, Friday beers, etc). - Developers can create profiles (add a small bio and upload their skills) so companies can find them, too. - If logged-in, you can filter by recommendations. - Dark mode.

Very much looking forward!
